Class ShoppingBag

java.lang.Object
ShoppingBag
All Implemented Interfaces:
ICollection
public class ShoppingBag extends Object implements ICollection
ShoppingBag class is used to track items in a shopping bag. When an item is placed in an empty bag, it is placed at the bottom of the bag, then we place another item on top of it and so on until the bag is full. When emptying a bag, we start with the item on top then the next until the bag is empty.
